{"tid":2401425,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衞生署以月薪最高13.5萬請退休警追隨病例 入職要求是退休督察或以上","createTime":"2021-02-09T16:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T04:17:22.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c98e56e020eb963b14e428d44b16af76b695baa4","tid":2401425,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T16:59:27.000Z","msg":"作為控疫主要部門的衞生署事事慢半拍，近日疫情大幅放緩，才增聘人手處理各類流行病學追查等工作。但本報發現，其中7個合約期6個月至1年的調查員以至指揮官等職位，均只聘請退休警務人員，涵蓋職級下至警員上至高級警司，最高月薪達13.5萬元兼享15%約滿酬金。衞生署未有回覆各職位請人數目，但假設各職位只請一人，涉及薪酬開支已達4,275,880元。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》曾向衞生署查詢每個職位會聘用多少人、招聘理由及依據。衞生署僅覆稱，為處理疫情及保障公共衞生，一直透過不同途徑增聘人手，包括聘用四大紀律部隊在內的退休公務員。<br />\n署方沒有透露7個職位各請多少人，但表示截至今年2月9日，已聘請160名全職退休警，負責協助執行防疫抗疫，及有關《吸煙（公眾衞生）條例》和《2018年應課稅品（修訂）條例》的工作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/FLJD2YOYQFD47OEZIFUTNUWBNQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR20bQAQty97VikZ7Ih6hrIeM8QY88ld1okTEYZfRwGWdlZ6JB-C8r4cNIE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FFLJD2YOYQFD47OEZIFUTNUWBNQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR20bQAQty97VikZ7Ih6hrIeM8QY88ld1okTEYZfRwGWdlZ6JB-C8r4cNIE&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQklZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=cc1f3db7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210210%2FFLJD2YOYQFD47OEZIFUTNUWBNQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR20bQAQty97VikZ7Ih6hrIeM8QY88ld1okTEYZfRwGWdlZ6JB-C8r4cNIE&h=89ffbc28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210210/FLJD2YOYQFD47OEZIFUTNUWBNQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR20bQAQty97VikZ7Ih6hrIeM8QY88l